publisher			Bigger Boat 							
publish_time	 2015年2月27日		
desc_long							评测						“It's the indie puzzle game we've all been waiting for.”Jay Is Games“Painterly puzzle game wants to twist your brain into knots. [...] Stuck? You don't have to start all over. Just rewind a bit.”Game Walkers												关于这款游戏							Do you love games that provide true mental challenge?Rainbow Hero is a clever 2D puzzle game where levels may seem impossible at first glance but ingeniously simple when you've figured it out.The rules are simple yet each challenge will require thoughtful solutions. Best of all, Rainbow Hero lets you turn back time so you can never become stuck! Experiment and try new approaches to find your way through every level.Rainbow Hero combines multiple game mechanics such as:Travel on multi-directional platforms until they hit obstacles.Teleport characters or their items. Reflect the lasers off walls to clear the path. Control two characters simultaneously with added depth for puzzle solving. Unlock hidden passages, bounce balls, rotate parts of the world and a lot more!						
title	 Rainbow Hero			
